## <a id="pattern-groups"></a>Pattern Groups (fleet-wide chart fixes)

These deployments share a name prefix and a priority bucket — usually instances
of the same Helm chart or operator. **Fix the chart once instead of filing N
separate tickets.**

> Detail-section workloads in groups with N≥10 instances are collapsed below
> the first card with a `+ N-1 identical instances` note. Click through to the
> CSV for full per-instance metrics.

